%2FldfuzA7j4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=13a5ebff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/04/03/hk-tv-audience-measurement2/wireless-home/</a><br />\n<br />\n✨都市傳說，未經Fact check：<br />\n收視公司偏幫TVB係出哂名<br />\n<br />\n#全城轉台運動 #tvb借疫情翻身<br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"7488d58a25a2dc6f46556a57112ff7a1026aa574","tid":1924172,"uid":208412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T13:55:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"88e2c3c0ec66bb5a1fcc822ecd93304765a19434","tid":1924172,"uid":208412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T13:55:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d110634c6c25b6780c4c67d6ef46b6814165645e","tid":1924172,"uid":208412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T13:55:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4cb5771414623e8fd86c25fe727db951d23e725b","tid":1924172,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T13:55:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f56ac1d825950b6b77792aeac46e0ae8ae8dcbb","tid":1924172,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T13:56:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"50f77d3605bd077c686e33a252cc2f3f36cc2794","tid":1924172,"uid":208412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T13:56:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9307b3eec3b57ca2eb6b09b7fd3bf505062ee95d","tid":1924172,"uid":1410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T13:57:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b1ec5cbce7187615ea3e3eb91e430ea3310695","tid":1924172,"uid":1410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T13:57:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a1b33f25cfbccd26262de929f8aa51892ba2d5d","tid":1924172,"uid":208412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"